cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques to separate layers in a scene captured via light field imaging. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves 3D geometry estimation, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). The use of regularization techniques and optimization algorithms suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper involves the use of machine learning techniques to solve the problem, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
